1939;;The Nursemaid Who Disappeared;;British;;Arthur B. Woods;;Arthur Margetson, Peter Coke;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Nursemaid_Who_Disappeared;;In this thriller, a playwright overhears a gang of men plotting a kidnapping and enlists the assistance of a detective to investigate them. They soon find the ring is fronted by a bogus employment agency that sends "clients" to check out potential victims. Action ensues as they endeavor to stop them.[4]